    public interface Window
extends EventBased
    This is the main window-class. All other windows extend from this class. With this window, you are only able to open this window to a player. When you create a new window, the user is not set before opening the window in the Setup.
    Since:
    2.3.3
    Author:
    Rincewind34
    See Also:
    WindowNameable
